quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  28,6,"Men weeЙ“inirana Й“e ka leydi, waЙ—ugol Й“e fewjooЙ“e e mayre, Men holla Fir'awna e Haamaana Й“uroowo wallude mo on ka laamu, wonndude e koneeli maЙ“Й“e wallayЙ—i Й“e Й—in, ko Й“e hulaynoo wata iwugol laamu maaЙ“e ngun, ngu re'ora e junngo gorko jibinaaЙ—o ka Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila."
  28,7,"Men lonngini neene Muusaa on (yo o his) Men wi'i: muynin mo si a hulii Fir'awna e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wata Й“e waru mo, haray waЙ—u mo e hontoore, werloЙ—aa nde ka caangol Nila, wata a hulu himo yooli wata a hulu Fir'awna no waЙ—i mo goЙ—Й—um, wata a suno sabu seedugol e makko, Menen Men artiray mo ka maaЙ—a hara himo wuuri, Men waЙ—ay mo kadi jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Alla Й“en, Й“en Й“e O Nulata faade e tagu Makko ngun."
  28,8,"O Й—oftii ko Men lonngini mo kon, fii waЙ—ugol mo ka hontoore, bugoo mo ka caangol. YimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en yiiti mo, Й“e Жҙetti mo, fii ko Alla Muuyi kon yo laato: wonnde Muusaa wonoyay gaГұo Fir'awna, Alla liЙ“ira laamu makko ngun e junngo Muusaa, o wona addanyЙ—o Й“e suno. Pellet, Fir'awna e yaakoraaЙ—o makko on Haamaana e wallooЙ“e Й“en, Й“e wonuno bakondinirЙ“e sabu keeferaaku e bewre maЙ“Й“e, e bonnugol Й“e ngol ka leydi."
  28,9,"Nde Fir'awna faalanoo warugol mo, Й“eyngu makko wi'ani mo: Kun paykun, ko tubbirde welo-welo am e an kadi. Wata a waru mo, hino gasa ka o nafiroyay en golle, maa jogitoren mo Й“iЙ—Й—o ne'aaЙ—o men. Hari fewndo ontuma, Й“e anndaa wonnde laamu maЙ“Й“e ngun laniray e juuЙ—e on Й—on."
  28,10,"ЖҒernde yumma Muusaa nden wonti yeewunde, yejjiti kala fiyakuuji aduna, si wanaa fii Muusaa; tawi o accii muГұГұaade, haa o eЙ“Й“i feГұГұinngol wonnde ko Й“iЙ—Й—o makko non, hakkee ko fii on woni e makko, si wanaano Men tbintinornoo Й“ernde makko nden, muГұГұinngol, fii yo o laato e gomЙ—im- Й“e fawii e Joomi mun, muГұГұiiЙ“e e ko O Гұaawata kon."
  28,11,"Yumma Muusaa (yo o his) wi'ani banndiraawo makko on, Й“aawo o bugaade mo ka caangol: Jokkitu mo, anndaa ko Й“e waЙ—ata mo; o Жҙeewiri mo ka muutii, fii wata Й“e anndu fii makko on. Fewndo ontuma, hawri Fir'awna e yimЙ“e mun Й“en so'aa-anndude wonnde on jiwo, ko banndiraawo Muusaa, ko tefugol humpitoo fii makko tun addi mo."
  28,12,"Muusaa saltori e muuyaande Alla muynugol rewЙ“e Й“en, ko adii nde Min nduttata mbo e neene makko, nde banndiraawo makko on yi'unoo hiЙ“e rerЙ—i e muyninngol mo, o wi'ani Й“e: On accay mi tinndina on e yimЙ“e suudu, muyninooЙ“e mo dankoo mo, hara kadi ko laaЙ“anooЙ“e mo?"
  28,13,"Men artiri Muusaa ka yumma makko, fii no Й“ernde makko Й“uuЙ“ira yi'ugol ma gite e gite, hara o sunoraaki seedugol e makko ngol, e fii yo yumma makko anndu kadi pellet, fodoore Alla nden e artirgol mo Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on, ko goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un. Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa ndee fodoore, tawi kadi, gooto e maЙ“Й“e anndaa ko on woni yumma makko."